channel.description:
As topic says, in windows it works good.
That is deltascape.
thats the error: [code] npc.cfg: file not found. npcdrops.cfg: file not found. autospawn.cfg: file not found. item.cfg: file not found. globaldrops.cfg: file not found. doors.cfg: file not found. shops.cfg: file not found. [/code]
Richscape is working good so i dont know why that is not working good.
